name: Dark Sue 5/6
description:
Dark Sue, visiting divinity of Brugmansia  flowers and vines. Its crystalline and hypnotic entity  can take you to the gardens of Tartessos, where it is originally from; Its food the toxic plants vines, which contain toxic properties that it uses to become cristal, and fight against its older sisters, Litmus columbae who seeks to devour it eternally.
Piece 5/6 Realtime rendered and digitally hadsculpted
